{"type": "article", "id": 56815, "title": "炸薯条剩下的马铃薯皮，还能用作街头食品包装｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-09-26T22:42:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 45667, "name": "Deadgood"}, {"id": 2291, "name": "Alessi"}, {"id": 53041, "name": "Sitskie Design Studio"}, {"id": 53042, "name": "Michele De Lucchi"}, {"id": 53043, "name": "Philipp Schenk-Mischke"}, {"id": 53044, "name": "Simone Caronni"}, {"id": 53045, "name": "Paolo Stefano Gentile"}, {"id": 53046, "name": "Pietro Gaeli"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 129, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180926205258X3tY1pbzcOW92F4L.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Peel Saver by Simone Caronni, Paolo Stefano Gentile and Pietro Gaeli</h3><p>炸薯条是很多人的心头好，光是市面上流行的快餐品牌，每年都要消耗大量马铃薯，也留下大量马铃薯皮废料。意大利设计师 Simone Caronni, Paolo Stefano Gentile 和 Pietro Gaeli 为了将这些废料利用起来，决定把它们做成街头食品包装。</p><p>马铃薯皮由淀粉和纤维成分组成，经过浸渍和自然干燥后，具有相互粘合和硬化的能力。所获得的材料完全由生产废料制成，并且 100％可生物降解。使用后，包装可以有效地重新插入生物循环中，成为动物食物或植物肥料。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205324Hy8nBtQKZpa3j0V9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205333suXtzFg1OHmbflP5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707276\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205335d5XJjs0SFkVaT1wl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707276\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205336JzUBMLNdni1TbfVH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707276\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205337pwO8fUGAZcoXNVCK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707276\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/09/26/peel-saver-potato-skins-ecological-packaging-fries/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Process Plug-Ins. by Philipp Schenk-Mischke</h3><p>Philipp Schenk-Mischke 是伦敦皇家艺术学院的研究生，Process Plug-Ins. 是他在校期间的最后一个项目，包括一套陶瓷花瓶和一小部分家具，它模糊了日常用品和概念家具之间的界限。</p><p>Philipp Schenk-Mischke 希望通过使用 BTM Ceramics，分析它们的制作或使用方式，尝试重新诠释一些经典的花瓶造型。虽然大多数陶瓷只有在形成后才会单独做干燥处理，但是 Schenk-Mischke 会扭曲他的造型，将它们放在一种振动板上，轻轻摇动并将成型的部件振动成更有机的形状。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205457A0aIcVDKZ26nPoWu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205458LY3ZdCk9VuDX6nbJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205500vmlonaAHSOuEKLIR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809262055002qvefkVzIDhKQTij.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205500qvcnSzN6EXYjlJdb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205501I5FRBH7ePMcfbXYE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205502X3nIiVmS9ygB7R4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://schenkmischke.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Philipp Schenk-Mischke</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>New Fig Collection and a Credenza by Sitskie Design Studio for Vinyl Lovers</h3><p>底特律设计工作室 Sitskie 创立于 2012 年，创始人是一对夫妻档 Adam 和 Vanessa Friedman。他们的原则是，每件作品都要经过多次迭代后才会被推向市场，希望精心设计的家具能够经久耐用不过时。</p><p>最近，Sitskie 刚刚推出了新的 Fig 系列座椅和 Open 45 Credenza，亮点是一些微妙但独特的小细节。Open 45 Credenza 最初是为老式唱片爱好者量身而做的，模块化设计允许用户创建他们自己的个人设置，配置摆放扬声器、唱片以及书籍。专设的绳索通道隐藏杂乱的电缆等，保持柜体的简洁利落。</p><p>Fig 系列包括座椅和凳子，灵感皆是来自 Sitskie 办公室的无花果树。植物宽阔的叶子与固定它们的细茎一起被转化为椅子的设计，其中包括皮革面层压曲面板和弯曲钢框架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205635S7Eys0nir9MfRlxj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205635g3IiR5eBcOTSlmUA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809262056368T0KfAEdbD9PtlVh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205637SHcRlpyVZ3oW4LFx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926205637REIMgrQZkKcaYzAn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926210028ISm3LesArq415F8l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809262100331NvjIJLQl6rozuiY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.sitskie.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sitskie Design Studio</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Plissé Kettle by Michele De Lucchi for Alessi</h3><p>在意大利品牌 Alessi 的历史上，出现了各种各样的明星水壶，比如该品牌销量最好的 9093 kettle 水壶。最近，意大利设计师 Michele De Lucchi 为 Alessi 设计了一款名为 Plissé 的水壶，灵感汲取自建筑、设计和时尚等多个领域。</p><p>它类似于通过厚褶变成三维形状的织物，水壶采用由热塑性树脂制成的高级时装连衣裙的形式，提供了红色、灰色、白色和哑光黑色。这令人想到时装设计师运用面料时喜欢使用的各种褶皱。</p><p>除了“褶皱”的形态，Plissé 水壶也很易于打开和关闭，并配备了防水垢过滤器。水壶使用简单，并配有安全装置，如果内部水量太少或没有水，就会切断电源。它的底座是隔热的，所以即使水达到沸点，它也可以安全地放在任何表面上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809262101341cbEQ60SAzram8Zt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.125917\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926210135x2LwKYFZySm5h9t3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926210135oLArdpm3s14BeOVY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.477995\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926210138k6n2sWcZdMbmVQXh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.261614\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926210140bKFT9YDxru3hMNeI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926210144ZipO9l1kzQ4KDb3s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/michele-de-lucchi-plisse-kettle-alessi-09-25-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Hug Chair by Deadgood</h3><p>英国家具品牌 Deadgood 的最新作品，尝试了专利纸绳编织工艺 Lloyd Loom。这种工艺由美国人 Marshall Burns Lloyd 于 1917 年发明，已有 100 年历史，制作方式是在金属丝外绕上两层牛皮纸，然后编织成纸绳。</p><p>经过反复试验，Deadgood 发现可以通过将编织材料应用到靠近再生钢框架的胶合板外壳来运用编织材料，尝试制作了这把 Hug Chair，亮相最近的伦敦设计节。</p><p>这是现代风格的椅子与传统编织方式的融合。虽然 Hug Chair 采用传统的编织材料，但他们也做到了创造一种完美平衡和永恒的现代设计，提供餐椅和休闲椅两个版本。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809262102503NBLsdaqi4kfPpnG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926210252OkMCeG7chF4l9Xdo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926210252zOqr90ycdaxDGuLw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180926210252fhyEs8Hn0rxMzZYq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201809262103022YZ8isSvADxkI3pW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414844\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.deadgoodltd.co.uk/hug-armchair/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Deadgood</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}